        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Zend_Translate is too strict in the way it caches data. It would be nice if we had two additional global options:\n\n * {{boolean *cacheEnable*}} Should the translation adapter use the cache. Defaults to {{true}}.\n * {{string *cacheId*}} Id to be appended onto the generated cache id to allow developers to have more then one instance of a translation adapter. Defaults to an empty string.\n"
